  "title": "Clinic Assistant (6-month Contract)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><p>Welcome patients to the Centre by greeting them warmly.</p><p>Assist in preparing patients prior to imaging examinations.</p><p>Assist patients with changing and mobility as required.<br /><br />Escort patients to and from examination rooms and waiting areas.<br /><br />Support radiographers and nurses during examinations where required.<br /><br />Maintain patient confidentiality, privacy, and dignity at all times.</p><p>Follow Centre SOPs and regulatory guidelines.</p><p>Ensure a clean, safe, and organized clinical environment.</p><p>Maintain goodwill and professionalism with patients at all times.</p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><p>Minimum Diploma or equivalent</p><p>Prior experience in a clinic, healthcare, or customer service role is an advantage</p><p>Able to adapt quickly, multitask and work under tight deadlines</p><p>A team player with a positive and service-oriented attitude<br /><br />Ability to start immediate, with a 6-month renewable contractual term</p>",
